    {
      "content": "With Premium Storage, your applications can have up to 32 TB of storage per VM and achieve 50,000 IOPS (input/output operations per second) per VM with extremely low latencies for read operations.",
      "pos": [
        789,
        985
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This article gives you a guideline on how to migrate your disks, Virtual Machines (VMs) from on-premises or Standard Storage or a different cloud platform to Azure Premium Storage.",
