    {
      "content": "To get a detailed overview of the Azure Premium Storage offering check out <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Premium Storage: High-Performance Storage for Azure Virtual Machine Workloads<ept id=\"p1\">](storage-premium-storage-preview-portal.md)</ept>.",
