        5244,
        5263
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "By default, disk caching policy is <bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>Read-Only<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept> for all the Premium data disks, and <bpt id=\"p2\">*</bpt>Read-Write<ept id=\"p2\">*</ept> for the Premium operating system disk attached to the VM.",
